^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Ok, so the next question is, assuming you have 2-card or 3-card support, when should you think about bidding game? Well, let's first think about what partner can have and how many Bergen declarer points that translates to. We know for a fact that partner is promising 5-10 HCP and a 6-card suit. First of all, we can add 2 points for the six card length. So we are up to 7-12 Bergen starting points. Now we also have to take distribution into account. Let's look at the most common distributions for opener.|
