^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First is the 6-3-2-2 distribution as in this hand. In this case, you can add 1 for the doubleton and 1 for the sixth trump--12 Declarer Points. So, we are in the 9-14 declarer points range.|
