^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|It might occur to some of you that opener can have a quality suit (or even 2 quality suits when 6-4-2-1). But I don't tend to worry about those, because if partner's hand is close to 10 HCP and he has some quality suits, he would often open 1 rather than 2. So here is what I do.|
